{"tid":1754171,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[理大] 荃灣區議會當選人聯署","createTime":"2019-11-25T06:25:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T06:35:41.000Z","uid":96182,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d90a622b0c916a1d1902e6043b76b8ff5676a58a","tid":1754171,"uid":96182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T06:25:30.000Z","msg":"【聯署聲明】促請警方理大退場  立即回應五大訴求<br />\n<br />\n區議會選舉結束，數以百萬計選民再次以選票對特區政府發出非常清晰的聲音：香港人是不會屈服於警暴，更不會屈服於暴政下。香港人的訴求非常清楚：五大訴求，缺一不可。<br />\n<br />\n民意從來沒有逆轉。<br />\n<br />\n我們在選舉勝利的晚上，並沒有忘記一眾仍被困於理工大學的手足。據現場人士轉述，有不少被困手足現時已經出現精神錯亂等症狀；再者，天氣開始轉冷，食物開始短缺，衛生環境亦日趨惡劣，可見理大現場正毋庸置疑地出現一場人道危機。<br />\n<br />\n我們以荃灣區議會勝選人的身份，在此嚴正向特區政府要求：<br />\n<br />\n一、馬上勒令警方撤離現場；<br />\n二、容許各方進入理大範圍進行人道救援；<br />\n三、立即回應並落實五大訴求。<br />\n<br />\n荃灣區議會選舉當選人<br />\n劉肇軒  林錫添  陸靈中  岑敖暉  易承聰<br />\n陳劍琴  李洪波  劉卓裕  潘朗聰  譚凱邦<br />\n劉志雄  謝旻澤  趙恩來  賴文輝  黃家華<br />\n陳琬琛<br />\n2019年11月25日"},{"pid":"97fd2f7e66c6c096d0601c9ec621205622142005","tid":1754171,"uid":28812,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T06:25:51.000Z","msg":"ho ball !"},{"pid":"458d21d2b76aa7985e080a1ab28ebbb439e6897d","tid":1754171,"uid":96182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T06:27:31.000Z","msg":"開心左一個上晝<br />\n各區當選人一齊出聲啦！<br />\n唔好唔記得poly手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0fb3ece081344053f619a4f21014d3a33d7c407","tid":1754171,"uid":15730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T06:28:02.000Z","msg":"其他區快啲跟手做"},{"pid":"2ab63ab86627799755c8592cf0963c17c4d10853","tid":1754171,"uid":96182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f0fb3ece081344053f619a4f21014d3a33d7c407","tid":1754171,"uid":15730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T06:28:02.000Z","msg":"其他區快啲跟手做"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T06:33:48.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"da7bb8a2eb4a67a5f0c133c792673e45bb5e4615","tid":1754171,"uid":209248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T06:34:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f11f476931756703936c98bd8d279f3f3ba4b828","tid":1754171,"uid":228868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T06:34:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bd10af57edcf54f66067352b8ecf00107b1d7393","tid":1754171,"uid":228868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T06:34:52.000Z","msg":"識做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6279bd35a7e8be5b6c43738589e5d6a4bfc0959d","tid":1754171,"uid":58789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T06:35:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"99461b6edbdfe3b0e54c4533c518654d40e0855a","tid":1754171,"uid":53415,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T06:35:41.000Z","msg":"點解叫人投票?<br />\n因為我就係要呢喲"}]}